# Content SEO Kit — commends = execute

When the user references `.commends/TODO_article_reserch.md` or other kit commends files, execute the full workflow.

Before Phase 0:

1. Read `content-pipeline.profile.json` (paths, language, CTA, denylist)
2. Read `.content-kit/standards/*.md` (quality bar — same for every subject)
3. Run `node scripts/content-kit-sync.mjs check` — if kit drift, suggest `diff` then `update --approve`

Do not edit read-only commends headers. Project-specific SSOT (registry, routes, live content) is never overwritten by kit sync.
